snippet.title: Unbound: Worlds Apart - Kickstarter Trailer 2019
snippet.description:
Unbound: Worlds Apart campaign on Kickstarter will start on 7th of May 2019.
Check it on: http://unboundthegame.com/kickstarter

Unbound Worlds Apart is an upcoming indie game where you will summon magic portals to venture through different realms in order to bring justice to your world.

Meanwhile you can wishlist  the game on Steam: http://unboundthegame.com/steam

Find out more about Unbound: Worlds Apart:

Website: http://unboundthegame.com
Twitter: https://twitter.com/UnboundTheGame/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/UnboundGame/
Discord: https://discord.gg/3gU8Amb
#kickstarter #gaming #unbound #puzzlegame
